import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'app-acr-form', templateUrl: './acr-form.component.html', styleUrls: ['./acr-form.component.css'] }) export class AcrFormComponent implements OnInit { password = 'password'; confirmPassword = 'password'; showPassword = false; confirmShowPassword = false; constructor() { } ngOnInit() { } public showHidePass(type: string): void { if (type == 'password' && this.password === 'password') { this.password = 'text'; this.showPassword = true; } else { this.password = 'password'; this.showPassword = false; } if (type !== 'password' && this.confirmPassword === 'password') { this.confirmPassword = 'text'; this.confirmShowPassword = true; } else { this.confirmPassword = 'password'; this.confirmShowPassword = false; } } }
